Quizki deployment guide
-----------------------

Ensure there is a remote added for git for production and staging
 git remote add quizkistaging ssh://53251221e0b8cd963f000108@quizkistaging1-quizki.rhcloud.com/~/git/quizkistaging1.git/
 git remote add quizkiprod ssh://b18cc03486ab440a8bb764bf4f6d94b3@quizki-quizki.rhcloud.com/~/git/quizki.git/


To Push to Production:
 git push quizkiprod master:master

To push to Staging:
 git push quizkistaging staging:master


Until Issue #109 is addressed, you will need to ensure that persistence.xml and shiro.ini have correct jdbc urls.. You can check the value by ssh'ing to the server and running 'echo $OPENSHIFT_MYSQL_DB_HOST:$OPENSHIFT_MYSQL_DB_PORT'

